commit.message: Update copyright year in affected files since the change is non-trivial
Replace "canoize" with "canonicalize" in a code comment which left out in the code renaming
As a part of the rename from "canonize" to "canonicalize", doCanonize should also be renamed. This was an oversight in the original PR.
Move utilities from ParseUtil into Handler, rename to canonicalizeString, call file.length() only once.
Reduce allocation by deferring substring calls until canonizeString determines it is needed
